## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1 — Security + Performance (Low Risk, High Impact)

#### [MODIFY] [index.js](file:///c:/Users/Varad/AtomQuest/goalpulse-api/src/index.js)

- Add `express-rate-limit`:
  - Global: 200 req / 15 min
  - `/api/ai/*`: 20 req / 15 min (Groq quota protection — bump to 50 for demo if needed)
  - `/api/auth/login`: 10 req / 15 min (brute-force protection)
- Add `helmet()` for security headers (Content-Security-Policy, X-Frame-Options, etc.)

#### [MODIFY] [admin.js](file:///c:/Users/Varad/AtomQuest/goalpulse-api/src/routes/admin.js)

Fix `GET /completion` N+1:
- Fetch all sheets + goals + achievements in 3 **bulk** queries wrapped in `Promise.all`
- Build in-memory `Map` lookups indexed by `employee_id`
- Eliminates ~140 Supabase calls per request (for a 50-user org)

#### [MODIFY] [teams.js](file:///c:/Users/Varad/AtomQuest/goalpulse-api/src/routes/teams.js) — `enrichTeams`

Parallelize the 4 sequential calls:
```js
// BEFORE (sequential — 4 round-trips in series)
const memberRows = await supabase...
const goals = await supabase...
const achievements = await supabase...

// AFTER (parallel — 2 round-trips total)
const [memberRows, goals] = await Promise.all([supabase...members, supabase...goals]);
const achievements = goals.length ? await supabase...achievements : [];
```

#### [MODIFY] [goals.js](file:///c:/Users/Varad/AtomQuest/goalpulse-api/src/routes/goals.js)

- Add input length guards: title ≤ 200 chars, description ≤ 1000 chars, target_value ≤ 100 chars
- Verify team membership explicitly when `team_id` is provided (403 if not a member or manager)

