### Phase 2 — Team Goals Backend

#### [MODIFY] [teams.js](file:///c:/Users/Varad/AtomQuest/goalpulse-api/src/routes/teams.js)

**Add `POST /api/teams/:teamId/goals`**
- Auth: caller must be an active member OR manager of the team
- Finds/creates the caller's goal sheet for the active cycle
- Enforces BRD: max 8 goals, min 10% weightage, 100% total cap
- Inserts goal with `team_id` set for team-scoped queries

**Add `PATCH /api/teams/:teamId/goals/:goalId`**
- Validates ownership: goal must belong to the caller's goal sheet
- Sheet must be in DRAFT or REJECTED status (not locked)
- Updates title, description, target_value, weightage, thrust_area

**Add `DELETE /api/teams/:teamId/goals/:goalId`**
- Validates ownership
- Sheet must not be APPROVED or PENDING_APPROVAL
- Deletes goal, logs to audit_log

